<plot>A resourceful little girl entranced by the top prize of a large stuffed bear, is determined to win her school fundraiser without the help of her disapproving father. Follow Natalie on this Disney like adventure as she travels through the streets looking for someone to lend her a hand. But Disney never ended a story like this as she ironically finds her savior in the last place she could have ever expected.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?653092</url></doc>
